Things I am working on at the moment&hellip;
CyberSecLab - Terraform, Ansible and Python scripts for an offensive security lab in AWS
Inspired by Rob and his Shiva project to automatically create an attack ready ubuntu host, I decided to expand on the concept and automate the deployment of not only an attack host, but an environment where you can perform all manner of cyber-sec activities from anywhere you choose has an internet connection.
